values:
Count the days..I think thats how late she was and how scared I was for those days...Turns out she's not..and I can rest a bit easy now...

Phew...

check out www.debutfilm.com

and Congrats again to my online homeboy Charlie for taying the big knot...dunno if I could have done that at age 19..(still dunno if I could do it now)

Is she or isnt she?  I'm stressing so bad because of this.  I guess I'll find out tonight, before I make it public to the world.

Hey want to see me with blue hair?

Go here:
http://members.pinoypower.com/Rockstyle/caughtblue.jpg

http://members.pinoypower.com/Rockstyle/stickereating.jpg

I was starving, so I bought some crap at 7-11 today...the Big Bite Hot Dogs actually looked tasty...the clerk refused to sell it to me... "These have been out since 9:00 am, trust me, you don't want to buy these things" what a nice guy... want to see the pics *N* and I took ?

Nothing is going right today...everything irratates me...my plans..aren't going according to schedule...everything got fucked up today and I look like shit.  I didn't fix myself right today because I thought that I could go se my barber early and get back home in time to clean up...Barber not in..throws off the rest of everything I had meticuously planned today.  Now I am at work, still looking like I just woke up and I am attempting to be cheery..

It's not happening..

Next time *N* says that she should probably be getting home now, I should listen...

Trouble brews and begins..

When it's slow, and you wish you were out, but you can't find a thing to do or a person to conversate with, so you rely on the net, only to find a place just as empty as the real world?

Just one of those days..

Wow...Just looking over other people's journals..pretty interesting stuff..

I guess this thing can get sort of addicting.

My hands..still cold..my bladder..still full..my head..still in thought..my dog...still sleeping..

Ok, I am here at work..typing my first entry here in my Livejournal.  What to say, what to say.  It's pretty sunny here in my beautiful city of San Francisco, but my hands are freezing as it is fu*king cold here at my place at work.  My girlfriend *N* and I took some studio photos the other day and we received them today.  I have to say that I felt very happy with the way they came out.  I wish I could have kept all of the pictures but alas, we only could choose two.  

Next time we take pictures, I'll try and not look so damn preppy, and I will be sure to include my beautiful blue dyed hair in those future pictures.

BTW can anyone help me write some songs?
